      "rationale": "Ansys Mechanical passes NAFEMS benchmark LE1 (plane stress), LE10 (thick cylinder), and contact patch test to within 0.5% of analytical solutions. Code verification documentation is part of the Ansys verification manual (release 2022 R2) and was reviewed by the assessment team."
