      "rationale": "Validation performed on the exact non-cannulated 7.5 mm pedicle screw geometry and material lot intended for submission. ASTM F1717 test configuration replicates the posterior spinal fixation loading mode. No extrapolation beyond the validated geometry or loading regime is claimed in the submission. Validation domain fully encompasses the COU."
    }
